snippet.title: Command & Conquer™: Legions | Red Alert Season Trailer | Into The Infinite 2024
snippet.description:
Command & Conquer™: Legions, the latest EA-licensed C&C mobile strategy game, is launching globally soon. Stay tuned for the new Red Alert season and conquer new territories! Lead your army to victory with iconic units, powerful weapons, and strategic gameplay. Dominate your enemies and customize your base in this thrilling mobile strategy game. #CNCLegions #CommandandConquer #StrategyGames

Pre-register now: www.cnclegions.com
